UC-01: Submit Raw Idea
Actor: User
Description: User enters unstructured text input into the system
Preconditions:
User is on the input interface
Postconditions:
Input is sent to backend for analysis

Main Flow:

User types/pastes idea
User clicks submit
System sends input to controller

Alternate Flow:

If input is empty -> system shows error message

UC-02: Detect and Clarify Unsure Input
Actor: System, User
Description: System detects unsure input and asks clarification questions
Preconditions:
Input received from user
Postconditions:
Clarified input is prepared

Main Flow:

Controller checks input length/quality
If it is unstrucutred -> triggers Clarifier Agent
System generates questions
User answers questions
System combines answers with input



UC-02: Generate Strategic Plan
Actor: System
Description: Planner Agent creates phases and milestones
Preconditions:
Clarified input available
Postconditions:
List of phases generated

Main Flow:

Input sent to Planner Agent
Agent generates roadmap (phases, steps)
Output stored for next stage


UC-03: Structure Mind Map
Actor: System
Description: Structurer Agent converts plan into hierarchical structure
Preconditions:
Planner output available
Postconditions:
Nested JSON tree created

Main Flow:

Receive phases(steps) list
Convert into parent-child hierarchy
Output structured JSON


UC-04: Validate Structure
Actor: System
Description: Validator ensures JSON format and logic correctness
Preconditions:
Structured JSON available
Postconditions:
Validated or corrected JSON

Main Flow:

Parse JSON
Check required keys
Validate hierarchy

Alternate Flow:

2a. If invalid -> return error or regenerate



UC-05: Enhance Mind Map
Actor: System
Description: Enhancer improves visual and semantic quality
Preconditions:
Validated JSON available
Postconditions:
Styled and enriched JSON

Main Flow:

Add colors, emojis, summaries
Improve readability
Output enhanced structure


UC-06: Visualize Mind Map
Actor: System
Description: Render mind map using visualization engine
Preconditions:
Enhanced JSON available
Postconditions:
Interactive mind map displayed

Main Flow:

Send JSON to renderer
Generate visual graph
Display to user


UC-07: Export Mind Map
Actor: User
Description: User downloads generated mind map
Preconditions:
Mind map displayed
Postconditions:
File downloaded

Main Flow:

User selects format (PNG/PDF/JSON)
System processes export
File downloaded


UC-08: End-to-End Mind Map Generation
Actor: User, System
Description: Complete flow from input to export
Preconditions:
User accesses system
Postconditions:
Mind map generated and optionally downloaded

Main Flow:

User submits idea
System checks vagueness
Clarification (if needed)
Planner - Structurer - Validator - Enhancer
Visualization displayed
User exports output


UC-09: Refine Mind Map (Single Iteration)
Actor: User, System
Description: User refines the generated mind map by providing updated input or feedback, and the system regenerates the mind map once.
Preconditions:
Initial mind map has been generated and displayed
Postconditions:
Updated (refined) mind map is generated and displayed

Main FLow:
User reviews the generated mind map
User provides refinement input (e.g., adds more details / corrects idea)
System receives updated input
System re-runs pipeline (Planner - Structurer - Validator - Enhancer)
Updated mind map is generated
System displays refined mind map

Alternate Flow:
9a. If user provides empty refinement then system shows error message
9b. If regeneration fails then system shows previous version with error notification